188 //calculate cost between to reach child node if travelling through parent node
189  double calculate_cost (node* parent_node, node* child_node) //
190  {
191  double cost;
192  if (check_line_obstacle(parent_node->point,child_node->point)) {
193  cost=INFINITY;
194  } else if(parent_node->parent == NULL) {
195  cost=get_dist(parent_node->point,child_node->point);
196  } else {
197  cost=calculate_cost(parent_node->parent,parent_node)+get_dist(parent_node->point,child_node->point);
198  }
199  return(cost);
200  }

286  //function to find lowest cost neighbours of new point
287  node* check_neighbours (geometry_msgs::Point new_point){
288  if (debugging){
289  ROS_INFO("I've entered check neighbours");
290  }
291  neighbours.clear();
292  double cost_from_neighbour,total_cost;
293  double lowest_cost=INFINITY;
294  double x_diff,y_diff;
295  find_neighbours(new_point);
296  node* lowest_cost_neighbour=NULL;
297  for (int i = 0;i<neighbours.size();i++){
298  x_diff=new_point.x-neighbours[i]->point.x;
299  y_diff=new_point.y-neighbours[i]->point.y;
300  if (abs(x_diff) <= node_dist && abs(y_diff)<=node_dist){
301  cost_from_neighbour=sqrt(pow(y_diff,2)+pow(x_diff,2));
302  if(cost_from_neighbour <= node_dist && !check_line_obstacle(new_point,neighbours[i]->point)){
303  total_cost=get_cost(neighbours[i])+cost_from_neighbour;
304  if (total_cost < lowest_cost){
305  lowest_cost_neighbour=neighbours[i];
306  lowest_cost=total_cost;
307  }
308  }
309  }
310  }
311 
312  return(lowest_cost_neighbour);
313  }

315  //function to rewire neighbour nodes to test_node
316  void rewire_neighbours (node* test_node) {
317  if (debugging){
318  ROS_INFO("I've entered rewire neighbours");
319  }
320  double total_cost;
321  for (int i = 0;i<neighbours.size();i++){
322  total_cost=calculate_cost(test_node,neighbours[i]);
323  if (total_cost < get_cost(neighbours[i]) && !check_line_obstacle(test_node->point,neighbours[i]->point) && (get_dist(test_node->point,neighbours[i]->point) <= node_dist)){
324  remove_child_from_parent(neighbours[i]);
325  neighbours[i]->parent=test_node;
326  neighbours[i]->cost=total_cost;
327  }
328  }
329 
330  return;

366  //function to find neighbours based on grid-based-spacial indexing
367  void find_neighbours(geometry_msgs::Point temp_point){
368  if (debugging){
369  ROS_INFO("I've entered find_neighbours");
370  }
371  int lower_x_grid,upper_x_grid,lower_y_grid,upper_y_grid;
372  path_planning::grid_cell grid=find_grid_cell_for_spatial_indexing(temp_point);
373  //ROS_INFO("test point is (%lf,%lf)",temp_point.x,temp_point.y);
374  //ROS_INFO("grid is (%d,%d)",grid.x,grid.y);
375  neighbours.clear();
376 
377 
378  int search_width=0;
379  while(neighbours.empty()){
380  search_width++;
381  //restrict grid exceeding vector bounds
382  if((grid.x-search_width)<0){
383  lower_x_grid=0;
384  } else {
385  lower_x_grid=grid.x-search_width;
386  }
387  if((grid.x+search_width)>(GRID_WIDTH-1)){
388  upper_x_grid=(GRID_WIDTH-1);
389  } else{
390  upper_x_grid=grid.x+search_width;
391  }
392  if((grid.y-search_width)<0){
393  lower_y_grid=0;
394  } else {
395  lower_y_grid=grid.y-search_width;
396  }
397  if((grid.y+search_width)>(GRID_HEIGHT-1)){
398  upper_y_grid=(GRID_HEIGHT-1);
399  } else {
400  upper_y_grid=grid.y+search_width;
401  }
402  //ROS_INFO("X range (%d,%d)",lower_x_grid,upper_x_grid);
403  //ROS_INFO("Y range (%d,%d)",lower_y_grid,upper_y_grid);
404 
405  for(int i=lower_x_grid;i <= upper_x_grid;i++){
406  for (int j=lower_y_grid;j <=upper_y_grid;j++){
407  //ROS_INFO("Checking grid (%d,%d)",i,j);
408  for(int k=0; k < spatial_grid[i][j].size();k++){
409  //ROS_INFO("spacial_index (%d,%d) point (%lf,%lf)",i,j,spatial_grid[i][j].at(k)->point.x,spatial_grid[i][j].at(k)->point.y);
410  neighbours.push_back(spatial_grid[i][j].at(k));
411  }
412  }
413  }
414  }
415 
416  if (debugging){
417  ROS_INFO("im leaving find neighbour");
418  }
419  }

450  //function to determine if goal is found
451  void is_goal_found(){
452  if (debugging){
453  ROS_INFO("I've entered is goal found");
454  }
455  if (get_dist(root->point,goal) > goal_radius){
456  clear_goal_variables();
457  double x_diff,y_diff,cost_to_goal;
458  find_neighbours(goal);
459  for (int i = 0;i<neighbours.size();i++){
460  x_diff=goal.x-neighbours[i]->point.x;
461  y_diff=goal.y-neighbours[i]->point.y;
462  if (abs(x_diff) <= goal_radius && abs(y_diff) <= goal_radius){
463  cost_to_goal=sqrt(pow(y_diff,2)+pow(x_diff,2));

480  //function to find the shortest path to goal
481  std::vector<geometry_msgs::Point> find_path() {
482  if (debugging){
483  ROS_INFO("I've entered find path");
484  }
485  path_cost=get_cost(goal_node)+get_dist(goal_node->point,goal);
486  for (int i=0;i<goal_list.size();i++){
487  if ((get_cost(goal_node)+get_dist(goal_node->point,goal)) > (get_cost(goal_list[i])+get_dist(goal_node->point,goal))){
488  goal_node=goal_list[i];
489  }
490  }
491 
492  if (path_cost > (goal_node->cost + get_dist(goal_node->point,goal))){
493  path_cost=goal_node->cost + get_dist(goal_node->point,goal);
494  geometry_msgs::Point temp_point;
495  path.clear();
496  path_nodes.clear();
497  node* node_ptr = goal_node;
498  temp_point.x=node_ptr->point.x;
499  temp_point.y=node_ptr->point.y;
500  path.push_back(goal);
501  path.push_back(temp_point);
502  path_nodes.push_back(node_ptr);
503  while(node_ptr->parent != NULL)
504  {
505  node_ptr=get_parent(node_ptr);
506  temp_point.x=node_ptr->point.x;
507  temp_point.y=node_ptr->point.y;
508  path.push_back(temp_point);
509  path_nodes.push_back(node_ptr);
510  }
511  }
512  if (debugging){
513  ROS_INFO("I've exited find path");
514  }
515  return(path);
516 
517  }

538  //function to if check line between points is free on map. Based on Bresenham's lins algorithm
539  bool check_line_obstacle (geometry_msgs::Point point_1, geometry_msgs::Point point_2) {
540  /*if (debugging){
541  ROS_INFO("I've entered check line obstacle");
542  }*/
543  geometry_msgs::Point test_point_1,test_point_2;
544  path_planning::grid_cell grid_1,grid_2,grid_1_test,grid_2_test;
545  int difference_x,difference_y;
546  int map_test;
547  double grad, c,x_test,y_test,angle;
548  if(point_1.x > point_2.x){
549  test_point_1=point_2;
550  test_point_2=point_1;
551  }else {
552  test_point_1=point_1;
553  test_point_2=point_2;
554  }
555  grad=(test_point_2.y-test_point_1.y)/(test_point_2.x-test_point_1.x);
556  c=(test_point_2.y-grad*test_point_2.x);
557  angle=atan(grad);
558 
559  grid_1=find_grid_cell(test_point_1);
560  grid_2=find_grid_cell(test_point_2);
561  difference_x=grid_2.x-grid_1.x;
562  difference_y=grid_2.y-grid_1.y;
563  if (test_point_1.x==test_point_2.x){
564  if (difference_y >= 0) {
565  for(int i = grid_1.y+1; i < grid_1.y+difference_y+1; i++) {
566  grid_2_test.x=grid_2.x;
567  grid_1_test.x=grid_1.x;
568  grid_2_test.y=i;
569  grid_1_test.y=i-1;
570  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
571  return(true);
572  }
573  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
574  return(true);
575  }
576  }
577  } else if (difference_y < 0){
578  for(int i = grid_1.y; i > grid_2.y; i--) {
579  grid_2_test.x=grid_2.x;
580  grid_1_test.x=grid_1.x;
581  grid_2_test.y=i;
582  grid_1_test.y=i-1;
583  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
584  return(true);
585  }
586  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
587  return(true);
588  }
589  }
590  }
591  } else if (difference_y >= 0) {
592  if (angle < PI/4){
593  for(int i = grid_1.x+1; i < grid_1.x+difference_x+1; i++) {
594  y_test=(grad*i*map_resolution)+c;
595  grid_2_test.y=int(y_test/map_resolution);
596  grid_1_test.y=int(y_test/map_resolution);
597  grid_2_test.x=i;
598  grid_1_test.x=i-1;
599  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
600  return(true);
601  }
602  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
603  return(true);
604  }
605  }
606  } else {
607  for(int i = grid_1.y+1; i < grid_1.y+difference_y+1; i++) {
608  x_test=((i*map_resolution)-c)/grad;
609  grid_2_test.x=int(x_test/map_resolution);
610  grid_1_test.x=int(x_test/map_resolution);
611  grid_2_test.y=i;
612  grid_1_test.y=i-1;
613  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
614  return(true);
615  }
616  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
617  return(true);
618  }
619  }
620  }
621  } else if (difference_y<0) {
622  if (angle > -PI/4){
623  for(int i = grid_1.x+1; i < grid_1.x+difference_x+1; i++) {
624 
625  y_test=(grad*i*map_resolution)+c;
626  grid_2_test.y=int(y_test/map_resolution);
627  grid_1_test.y=int(y_test/map_resolution);
628  grid_2_test.x=i;
629  grid_1_test.x=i-1;
630  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
631  return(true);
632  }
633  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
634  return(true);
635  }
636  }
637  } else {
638  for(int i = grid_1.y; i > grid_2.y; i--) {
639  x_test=((i*map_resolution)-c)/grad;
640  grid_2_test.x=int(x_test/map_resolution);
641  grid_1_test.x=int(x_test/map_resolution);
642  grid_2_test.y=i;
643  grid_1_test.y=i-1;
644  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_1_test)) {
645  return(true);
646  }
647  if(check_grid_for_obs(grid_2_test)) {
648  return(true);
649  }
650  }
651  }
652 
653  }
654  /*if (debugging){
655  ROS_INFO("I've exited check line obstacle");
656  }*/
657  return(false);
658 }
659  //function to check map if map grid cell is occupied
660  bool check_grid_for_obs (path_planning::grid_cell grid) {
661  int map_array_value=grid.y*map_width+grid.x;
662  if (map[map_array_value] > OBSTACLE_THRESHOLD || map[map_array_value] == -1) {
663  return(true);
664  } else {
665  return (false);
666  }
667  }

669  //function to add node to spatial index

671  if (debugging){
672  ROS_INFO("I've entered add_to_spatial_index");
673  }
674  path_planning::grid_cell grid=find_grid_cell_for_spatial_indexing(temp_node->point);
675  spatial_grid[grid.x][grid.y].push_back(temp_node);
676  }

678  //function to update neighbour radius based on number of nodes in environment
679  void update_neighbour_radius(){
680  neighbour_radius=sqrt((SEARCH_AREA*double (density))/(PI*double(node_list.size())));
681  if (neighbour_radius<node_dist){
682  neighbour_radius=node_dist;
683  }
684  }
685 
686  //function to check if node density less that max density
687  bool check_node_density(){
688  if (neighbours.size() > density){
689  return (false);
690  } else {
691  return(true);
692  }
693  }
694 
695  //function to test distance between test point and node to determine if greater than node_dist
696  bool node_dist_check(geometry_msgs::Point test_point, node* closest) {
697  double dist=get_dist(closest->point,test_point);
698  if (dist > node_dist){
699  return(true);
700  } else {
701  return(false);
702  }
703  }
704 
705  double get_dist(geometry_msgs:: Point point_1, geometry_msgs::Point point_2){
706  double x_diff;
707  double y_diff;
708  double dist;
709  x_diff=point_1.x-point_2.x;
710  y_diff=point_1.y-point_2.y;
711  return(sqrt(pow(y_diff,2)+pow(x_diff,2)));
712  }
